    <body>
        <p>Tag defined as a number or a descriptive name that is unique to each <MadCap:variable name="General.changeset" />. Requires the following format for the <code>calculate-checksum</code> command: <code>filepath::id::author</code>. Specify as <code>--changeset-identifier=value</code>. Positional format <code>&lt;command&gt; &lt;value&gt;</code> deprecated in 4.4+.</p>
        <p MadCap:conditions="exclude.future">In 4.24.??+, you can either specify <code>--changeset-identifier</code> in the <code>filepath::id::author</code> format or specify <code>--changeset-author</code>, <code>--changeset-id</code>, and <code>--changeset-path</code> individually.</p>
    </body>
</html>